          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Broker Callout -->
  <aside class="broker-callout">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="callout-content">
        <div class="callout-text">
          <h3>Our #1 MT4 Broker: AvaTrade</h3>
          <p>Multi-regulated (FCA, ASIC, CySEC), spreads from 0.9 pips, full EA support, and exclusive partner code available.</p>
        </div>
