            <p>It's a service that's very popular for traders looking to expand their trading volume or take a more "hands-off" approach to trading.</p>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Broker Tip:</strong> <a href="/brokers/etoro/">eToro</a> specializes in copy trading with their CopyTrader feature. For MT4 signals, <a href="/brokers/avatrade/">AvaTrade</a> offers excellent integration.
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">üè™</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">The MT4 Built-In Market</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>If you're looking for more technical indicators on your chart, you don't have to exit MT4 to find them.</p>
            <p>MT4 has a built-in market where you can purchase more than 1,700 trading robots and Expert Advisors. You can also add to your indicators arsenal with the over 2,100 technical indicators that MetaTrader 4 provides.</p>
            <p><strong>The best part? Many are absolutely free!</strong></p>
            <p>Access the marketplace directly from MT4 by clicking the "Market" tab at the bottom of the terminal window.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">ü§ñ</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">Algorithmic Trading & Expert Advisors</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>MT4 became popular mainly due to the ability for end-users to write their own trading scripts and robots (Expert Advisors) that could automate trading. This is a key feature of the platform.</p>
            <p>Once you're familiar with your MT4, almost anything you want can be implemented on it. You can leverage the opportunities provided by the Expert Advisors for automated trading. The Expert Advisor features robots that assist with both market forecasting, market analysis, and trading.</p>
            <p>MetaTrader 4 also provides you with the perfect environment for testing, developing, and optimizing new trading algorithms for all your trades on the market. You can post applications in the free code library or even sell them in the big-scale MetaTrader 4 market.</p>
            <div class="broker-note">
              <strong>Broker Tip:</strong> For running EAs 24/7, you'll need a VPS. <a href="/brokers/avatrade/">AvaTrade</a> and <a href="/brokers/axi/">Axi</a> offer free VPS hosting for qualified traders.
