            <p>No matter where you are, no matter where you're going, you're always a few clicks away from the world's largest market.</p>
            <p>The mobile apps are available for both iOS (iPhone/iPad) and Android devices, offering nearly all the functionality of the desktop version.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="accordion-item">
          <summary class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">üìä</span>
            <span class="accordion-title">Advanced Charting</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="accordion-content">
